author: COMSOL
description: This model first evaluates the effect of a direct-current (DC) applied potential on corrosion using a stationary analysis and then evaluates the effect of AC on corrosion using a transient analysis. The model is subsequently extended to investigate the effect of frequency on the AC corrosion rate, bringing out the double-layer capacitance contribution particularly at higher frequencies.
label: ac_corrosion.mph
